148	160	\N	Automobiles & Auto Components	{"pb_01": "information_available", "pb_02": "information_available", "pb_03": "information_available", "pb_04": "information_available", "pb_05": "information_available", "pb_06": "Information Available", "pb_07": "Information available", "pb_08": "information_available", "pb_09": "No clear information", "pb_10": "information_available", "pb_11": "information_available", "pb_12": "No clear information", "pb_13": "No LCA conducted", "pb_14": "information_available", "pb_15": "No clear information", "pb_16": "information_available", "pb_17": "information_available", "pb_18": "information_available", "pb_19": "information_available", "pb_20": "information_available", "pb_21": "information_available", "pb_22": "information_available", "pb_23": "information_available", "pb_24": "information_available", "pb_25": "information_available", "pb_26": "information_available", "pb_27": "information_available", "pb_28": "information_available", "pb_29": "information_available", "pb_30": "information_available", "pb_31": "No information", "pb_32": "information_available", "pb_33": "No clear information", "pb_34": "information_available", "pb_35": "information_available", "pb_01_textarea": "", "pb_02_textarea": "", "pb_03_textarea": "", "pb_04_textarea": "", "pb_05_textarea": "http://www.rolexrings.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Vigil-Mechanism-Policy-Whistle-Blower-Policy.pdf", "pb_06_textarea": "https://www.rolexrings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Code-of-Conduct-for-Directors-and-Senior-Management.pdf", "pb_07_textarea": "We don’t have any issues till date with regards to Human Rights, however if any such issue comes the HR Head shall look into it along with Any Director of the company. Issue is put before HR Head and then it is taken before Board of Directors.", "pb_08_textarea": "ESG Committee with Mr. Manesh Madeka as Chairman of the Committee", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "At Rolex Rings Limited, we adhere to a strict principle of upholding integrity at all times. Our commitment extends to full compliance with local regulations and laws in every country where we conduct business, and we firmly reject any form of corruption. Our company's Code of Ethics enforces a zero-tolerance policy towards corruption and emphasizes the importance of adhering to both legal requirements and our own business principles. Link to policy - https://www.rolexrings.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Vigil-Mechanism-Policy-Whistle-Blower-Policy.pdf", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "https://www.rolexrings.com/policies/", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "The company has a robust occupational health and safety management systems, and all the procedures are in place as per ISO 45001:2018. Additionally, the company is following the Rules and Regulations prescribed by the Government of the India to ensure health and safety. Regular monitoring of safety standards is done on shop floors.\\n\\nThe company uses systematic processes to detect and assess work-related hazards and risks on a regular and irregular basis. This includes doing daily checks on safety criteria such as equipment functionality and environmental conditions to quickly identify and minimize any hazards. In addition, we ensure that Personal Protective Equipment (PPE) kits are available and used properly to reduce threats to worker safety. Hazard risks are assessed using detailed evaluations that consider the nature of the work, potential exposure, and applicable legislation. The entity is committed to meeting Occupational Health and Safety (OHS) system requirements,\\nand it keeps records of hazard identification, risk assessments, and control measures to demonstrate its commitment to safety and regulatory compliance.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb