158	175	\N	Automobiles & Auto Components	{"pb_01": "information_available", "pb_02": "information_available", "pb_03": "information_available", "pb_04": "information_available", "pb_05": "information_available", "pb_06": "Information Available", "pb_07": "No clear information", "pb_08": "information_available", "pb_09": "Information available", "pb_10": "information_available", "pb_11": "information_available", "pb_12": "information_available", "pb_13": "No LCA conducted", "pb_14": "information_available", "pb_15": "information_available", "pb_16": "information_available", "pb_17": "information_available", "pb_18": "information_available", "pb_19": "information_available", "pb_20": "information_available", "pb_21": "information_available", "pb_22": "information_available", "pb_23": "information_available", "pb_24": "information_available", "pb_25": "information_available", "pb_26": "information_available", "pb_27": "information_available", "pb_28": "information_available", "pb_29": "information_available", "pb_30": "information_available", "pb_31": "information_available", "pb_32": "information_available", "pb_33": "No clear information", "pb_34": "information_available", "pb_35": "information_available", "pb_01_textarea": "", "pb_02_textarea": "", "pb_03_textarea": "", "pb_04_textarea": "", "pb_05_textarea": "https://www.lgb.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/whistle-blower-policy.pdf", "pb_06_textarea": "https://www.lgb.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/directors-senior-management.pdf", "pb_07_textarea": "https://www.lgb.co.in/about-us/sustainability/", "pb_08_textarea": "The CSR (Corporate Social Responsibility) committee focuses explicitly on responsibly operating socially,\\nenvironmentally, and ethically. It sets guidelines for the company to contribute to social welfare,\\nsupport environmental initiatives, and extend assistance to needy people, embodying LGB’s commitment to positively impacting society and promoting responsible business practices.", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "URL of the Policy: https://lgb.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/ANTI-BRIBERY-AND-CORRUPTION-POLICY.pdf", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "We are committed to fostering an inclusive and diverse workplace where all individuals are treated with\\nrespect and have equal opportunities for personal and professional growth. We firmly believe in providing\\nequal employment and advancement opportunities to all employees and applicants, regardless of their race, gender, ethnicity, religion, sexual orientation, caste, creed & color or disability. Our equal opportunity statement\\nguides our recruitment, hiring, training, promotion, and compensation practices, ensuring a fair and equitable\\nenvironment for everyone. We are dedicated to creating a workplace that celebrates diversity and promotes a\\nculture of inclusion, where each person’s unique talents and perspectives are valued and nurtured. The policy\\nis available on the Company’s intranet.", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes, Health and Safety is of utmost importance to LGB. The Company is certified with ISO – 45001 and ISO\\n14001 standards at all the plant and office locations. This standard enables organisation to provide safe and\\nhealthy workplaces by preventing work-related injury and ill health, as well as by proactively improving its\\nOccupational Health and Safety performance. Employees working at the plants are trained on environment,\\nhealth and safety best practices regularly and in accordance with the Company policy and local and statutory\\nregulations\\n\\nThe Company, as part of its Environment, health and safety management process implements Hazard\\nIdentification and Risk Assessment (HIRA) across all its activities - routine and non-routine. This process is\\naligned to the ISO 45001 standard and helps LGB in estimating the magnitude of potential risks and deciding\\nwhether risks identified are manageable or not.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "Yes, the Company has an Information Security Policy in place which ensures that all employees within the\\norganisation’s domain abide by the provisions of the policy regarding the security of data stored digitally within\\nits boundaries. It is also the commitment of the organisation to ensure information is kept confidential and\\nsecured. The policy is available on the Company’s intranet.", "pb_07_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "No board level, only operational level ESG committee/Individual", "pb_10_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "5", "pb_02_option_number2": "", "pb_03_option_number1": "18.19", "pb_03_option_number2": "0", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox1": "Employees", "pb_05_option_checkbox2": "Workers", "pb_05_option_checkbox3": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox4": "Value chain partners", "pb_05_option_checkbox5": "Customers", "pb_13_option_checkbox2": "", "pb_24_option1_checkbox": "", "pb_06_option1_checkbox1": "Code of conduct for Boa