20663) as the Chairman\\n2. Ms. Rama Bijapurkar, (Independent Non-Executive Director; DIN: 00001835)\\n3. Mr. Naresh Kumar Sethi, (Non-Executive Director; DIN: 08296486)\\n4. Mr. S. Thirumalai and (Non-Executive Director; DIN: 00011899)\\n5. Mr. Aditya Deb Gooptu (Managing Director & CEO; DIN: 07849104)", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "No, we have not conducted any Life Cycle Assessments for any of our products during the reporting period.", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "Although we do not have an equal opportunity policy in accordance with the Rights of Persons with\\nDisabilities Act, 2016, we strive to recruit the most qualified talent who share our values. We do not\\ndiscriminate based on age, color, disability, religion, caste, or sexual orientation during the recruitment\\nprocess", "pb_16_textarea": "NO female workers", "pb_17_textarea": "NO female workers", "pb_18_textarea": "NO female workers", "pb_19_textarea": "We have implemented ISO 45001:2018 occupational health and safety management system at our\\nmanufacturing units located at Azamabad and Toopran.\\n\\nWe undertake Hazard Identification and Risk Assessment (HIRA) on an annual basis and Job Safety\\nAnalysis for individual activities on a routine basis to identify work related hazards. We have developed\\ncontrol measures which are designed to mitigate the identified work-related hazards and record the same\\nin the risk register\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "NO other than permanent employees or workers.", "pb_23_textarea": "NO female workers.\\nNO other than permanent employees or workers.", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes, human right requirements are covered in business agreements and contracts with farmers through the\\nAgriculture Labor Practices (ALP) Code. Through implementation of the ALP code, we monitor and reviews\\nthe tobacco supply chain to prevent any form of discrimination including child labor, forced labour, payment\\nof minimum wages, as well as adherence to safe working conditions.", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "Converted to per crore INR of revenue", "pb_29_textarea": "Converted to per crore INR of revenue", "pb_30_textarea": "Converted to per crore INR of revenue", "pb_31_textarea": "Converted to per crore INR of revenue", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "We possess a comprehensive framework and policy addressing cybersecurity and data privacy risks. We\\nfirmly understand the loss or misuse of sensitive information, or its disclosure to outsiders, including\\ncompetitors and trading partners, could potentially have a significant adverse impact on our business\\noperations and potentially cause legal challenges in both monetary and non-monetary terms. Considering\\nthese potential impacts on us, we have put in place information technology policies and procedures which\\nare reviewed periodically. We also have established information technology controls like data backup\\nmechanism, disaster recovery centre, authorisation verification, etc. to protect the system", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_10_option_radio": "Company reported to have no such policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Company has no such policy in place", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "68.0", "pb_33_option_number": "0.0", "pb_02_option_number1": "0", "pb_02_option_number2": "0", "pb_03_option_number1": "16.67", "pb_03_option_number2": "0.0", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "", "pb_3