and honestly in all our business dealings in every office we have. This rule covers things like bribery, giving gifts, making payments to speed up processes, getting secret payments, and making political or charity donations. If anyone breaks these rules, they'll face serious consequences like fines, going to jail, or other strict punishments decided by our company.", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "", "pb_16_textarea": "There is no such employee association that is officially recognized by the Company.", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Occupational Health and Safety management system has been implemented at Gandhar Oil Refinery Ltd. The system covers all its employees and workers at all operational locations. Company has implemented Occupation Health and Safety Management System ISO: 45001:2018. Work-related hazards and risk assessments are identified using processes such as Hazard Risk analysis. Hazard Identification and Risk Assessment is conducted for all routine activities to identify work-related hazards. Job Safety Analyses are performed for non-routine tasks and new projects.", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "Working conditions - Done internally and also reviewed in customer audits.", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "Yes, the assurance has been carried out by ENEN Green Services Private Limited for BRSR FY 2023-24.", "pb_29_textarea": "Yes, the assurance has been carried out by ENEN Green Services Private Limited for BRSR FY 2023-24.", "pb_30_textarea": "Yes, the assurance has been carried out by ENEN Green Services Private Limited for BRSR FY 2023-24.", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "Yes, the company has data security and IT functioning policy. The policy complies with data protection law and follow good practice, protects the rights of staff, customers and partners, will clearly state how it stores and processes individuals’ data, protects all data on file from the risks of a data breach.", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "ESG/Sustainability function part of other board committee", "pb_10_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "100.0", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "0", "pb_02_option_number2": "0", "pb_03_option_number1": "33.34", "pb_03_option_number2": "20.0", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox1": "Employees", "pb_05_option_checkbox2": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox3": "Communities", "pb_05_option_checkbox4": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox5": "", "pb_13_option_checkbox2": "", "pb_24_option1_checkbox": "", "pb_06_option1_checkbox1": "Code of conduct for Board of Directors/KMPs", "pb_06_option2_checkbox2": "", "pb_14_option1_checkbox1": "", "pb_20_option1_checkbox1": "Lost Time Injury Frequency Rate", "pb_20_option1_checkbox2": "Fatalities", "pb_01_table_row1_number1": "87.39", "pb_01_table_row1_number2": "12.62", "pb_01_table_row1_number3": "100.0", "pb_01_table_row1_number4": "0.0", "pb_01_table_row2_number1": "", "pb_01_table_row2_number2": "", "pb_01_table_row2_number3": "", "pb_01_table_row2_number4": "", "