tasbank.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ESFB-Policy-on-Code-of-Conductof-Directors-January-2021.pdf\\n- For Senior Management: https://ir.equitasbank.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ESFB-Policy-for-Code-ofConduct-for-Senior-Management-Jan-2021.pdf\\n- For Employees: Available in the internal HR portal", "pb_07_textarea": "1. The Internal Complaints Committee (ICC) is dedicated to handling complaints related to sexual harassment and ensuring a safe and respectful workplace environment.\\n2. The Grievance Redressal Committee deals with all other concerns raised by our employees, offering a platform for the prompt resolution of various issues.                      If the grievance still remains unresolved, the employee can escalate the matter by contacting the Grievances Redressal Officer at grievance@equitasbank.com. The \\n grievances Redressal Officer, in consultation with the Grievance Redressal Committee, must resolve the issue within one week. If the employee is dissatisfied with this resolution, they may appeal to the Managing Director, who will provide a final decision within two weeks which will be binding on all parties concerned. ", "pb_08_textarea": "", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "false", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "No dedicated board committee, but MD/CEO/CFO/COO or any other executive with multiple responsibilities is also responsible for sustainability issues", "pb_10_