f the Company", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes. The health and safety management systems of the Company has been designed so as to ensure\\nthat the Company meets EHSMS (Environmental, Health, and Safety Management System) related legal\\nobligations and provides a safe and healthy working environment for its workers and employees.\\n\\nThe Company places highest importance for health and safety of employees and workers and hence, has\\nundertaken the following steps to identify work-related hazards and risk assessment :\\na. Internal Safety visits, which involve regular inspections of the workplace to identify potential\\nhazards and unsafe practices.\\nb. Elimination of Commonly Accepted Unsafe Practices.\\nc. Third Party Safety Audits.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_10_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "0.0", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "0", "pb_02_option_number2": "0", "pb_03_option_number1": "15.39", "pb_03_option_number2": "12.5", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox1