        Chairman\\n2      Dinesh Kumar Agarwal              Non-Executive Director               Member\\n3      Anil Jain                                    Executive Director                   Member", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "Yes, Refex Group of Company has the ABAC policy which is abiding for RIL also. Please refer to\\nhttps://www.refex. group/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Signed-ABAC-Policy.pdf\\nRIL has a policy of ‘zero tolerance’ of any practice that may be classified as corruption, bribery or giving or\\nreceipt of bribes. This policy is applicable to all individuals working at all levels and grades, including Board\\nMembers, Executive Directors and Senior Managerial Personnel (Senior Officers), Supervisory, Executive,\\nconsultants, interns, contractors, agency staff, agents or any other person associated with our Company and\\nsuch person acting on behalf of the Company.\\n\\nhttps://refex.co.in/pdf/Refex-Anti-Bribery-Anti-Corruption-Policy.pdf", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "No, we have not conducted LCA of any of our products or services.\\n", "pb_14_textarea": "The detailed spending amount is under review and will be available in the next financial year in the\\nrequisite formats.", "pb_15_textarea": "Yes, we have an equal opportunity policy as part of our overall HR policy as per the Rights of Persons with\\nDisabilities Act, 2016.", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes, Refex Industries Limited has an Occupational Health and Safety Management System (OHSMS) conforming to ISO 45001:2018 which has been successfully implemented and has covered 100 % of its operations, facilities, and offices\\n\\nThe Company has developed and implemented standard operating procedures (SOP) in line with ISO 45001:2018 to identify and control work-related hazards on a routine and non-routine basis. In our manufacturing unit and operations sites, this SOP is followed to identify risk and to implement control measures by the operation heads. They have to document the entire process which has been audited from time to time by internal auditors and also, 3rd party external auditors.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "Yes, sustainability data assurance is carried out by TUV India Private Limited.", "pb_29_textarea": "Yes, sustainability data assurance is carried out by TUV India Private Limited", "pb_30_textarea": "Yes, by TUV India Private Limited", "pb_31_textarea": "true", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "Not hosted on the website", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "No dedicated board committee, but MD/CEO/CFO/COO or any other executive with multiple responsibilities is also responsible for sustainability issues", "pb_10_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "0.0", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "0", "pb_02_option_number2": "0", "pb_03_option_number1": "33.34", "pb_03_option_number2": "66.67", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "Independent assessment/ evaluation/assurance has been carried out by an external agency", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "Ind