124	128	\N	Chemicals	{"pb_01": "information_available", "pb_02": "information_available", "pb_03": "information_available", "pb_04": "information_available", "pb_05": "information_available", "pb_06": "Information Available", "pb_07": "Information available", "pb_08": "information_available", "pb_09": "No clear information", "pb_10": "information_available", "pb_11": "information_available", "pb_12": "No clear information", "pb_13": "No LCA conducted", "pb_14": "No clear information", "pb_15": "information_available", "pb_16": "information_available", "pb_17": "information_available", "pb_18": "information_available", "pb_19": "information_available", "pb_20": "information_available", "pb_21": "information_available", "pb_22": "information_available", "pb_23": "information_available", "pb_24": "No information", "pb_25": "information_available", "pb_26": "information_available", "pb_27": "information_available", "pb_28": "information_available", "pb_29": "information_available", "pb_30": "information_available", "pb_31": "No information", "pb_32": "information_available", "pb_33": "No clear information", "pb_34": "information_available", "pb_35": "information_available", "pb_01_textarea": "", "pb_02_textarea": "", "pb_03_textarea": "", "pb_04_textarea": "", "pb_05_textarea": "mechanism not found for community.\\nWhistleblower mechanism available for all employees & Associates", "pb_06_textarea": "\\"This code is a commitment to ethical professional conduct by the Board of Directors and all employees of Foseco India Limited.\\"\\nhttps://fosecoindia.com/Policies.aspx", "pb_07_textarea": "", "pb_08_textarea": "The Business Responsibility performance is reviewed by the Board of Directors on an annual basis. During the year under review, the CSR Committee met one time, while the Stakeholders Relationship Committee of Directors met four times respectively, to take review and assess the Company’s performance in terms of Business Responsibility. The Board reviews these aspects as well.", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "The Company follows the Anti-Bribery and Corruption Policy (ABC Policy) framed by its Group Parent Company – Vesuvius plc. Vesuvius has a zero-tolerance approach to bribery and corruption. It is committed to the prevention, detection and investigation of all forms of bribery originating from the organisation or from third parties representing or associated with it. The policy for preventing bribery and corruption is the same around the world and the Company has taken the decision to hold itself up to the highest standards. The Anti-Bribery and Corruption Policy can be accessed at: https://www.vesuvius.com/en/supplier-portal/antibribery.html", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "The Company is currently not performing Life Cycle Assessments for its products. However, discussions regarding\\nthe same has been initiated.", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "Equal opportunity is covered as a part of Foseco India Code of Conduct. The Code of Conduct is displayed on the Company’s webpage at the following link -\\nhttps://fosecoindia.com/Policies.aspx", "pb_16_textarea": "no female workers", "pb_17_textarea": "NO female workers", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes, Foseco India Limited is certified for ISO 14001:2015 and ISO 45001:2018 standards. The company has implemented ISO Framework to provide a safe and healthy workplace across the company. This is done to prevent/ address work related injury, ill health and continuously improving safety performance to minimize risk. The company also has an occupational health center to address any safety concerns.\\n\\nThe company is certified for its environment management system in compliance with ISO 14001:2015 and ISO 45001:2018 standards. Foseco India Limited regularly conducts safety audits. Safety risk assessment is done for preventing any incidents, injuries, and hazards. Detailed Standard Operating Process (SOP) is referred before starting any new activity. Also hazard identification and risk analysis is done at regular intervals on ongoing basis.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "Company does not have other than permanent employees.", "pb_23_textarea": "Company does not have other than permanent employees.", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes, The Company has framed Anti-Sexual Harassment Policy. Relevant part of the said policy is laid in the business\\nagreement or contract which are required to be adhered", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "false", "pb_29_textarea": "false", "pb_30_textarea": "false", "pb_31_textarea": "Currently Scope 3 emissions are not\\nconsidered in the calculation of air emissions", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "There is no separate procurement policy where preference to purchase from suppliers comprising marginalized /\\nvulnerable groups is mentioned or factored", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "The Company’s parent organization – Vesuvius, has an adequate framework for maintaining and developing cyber security based on best practices and standards which is being followed by Foseco India. Monitoring of trends and cyber threats is constantly compared with current and multi-year plans supported by appropriate indicators to monitor progress on an ongoing basis. IT Security Strategy and Roadmap is based on ISO 27001 standard and NIST frameworks while the implementation takes place in the area of Preventive, Detective and Corrective controls. Progress has been made in the development of the security monitoring operations. Specialized cybersecurity tools are constantly being introduced and fine-tuned. Great emphasis is placed on user awareness by conducting a series of mandatory Cybersecurity training courses and implementing Phishing Campaigns. The Company continues to improve its Incident Handling and Response.", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "ESG/Sustainability function part of other board committee", "pb_10_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "0", "pb_02_option_number2": "0", "pb_03_option_number1": "33.34", "pb_03_option_number2": "0.0", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox1": "Employees", "pb_05_option_checkbox2": "Workers", "pb_05_option_checkbox3": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox4": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox5": "Customers", "pb_13_option_checkbox2": "", "pb_24_option1_checkbox": "", "pb_06_option1_checkbox1": "Code of conduct for Board of Directors/KMPs", "pb_06_option2_checkbox2": "Code of conduct for employees", "pb_14_option1_checkbox1": "", "pb_20_option1_checkbox1": "Lost Time Injury Frequency Rate", "pb_20_option1_checkbox2": "Fatalities", "pb_01_table_row1_number1": "92.43", "pb_01_table_row1_number2": "7.58", "pb_01_table_row1_number3": "100.0", "pb_01_table_row1_number4": "0.0", "pb_01_table_row2_number1": "", "pb_01_table_row2_number2": "", "pb_01_table_row2_number3": "100.0", "pb_01_table_row2_number4": "0.0", "pb_01_table_row3_number1": "92.43", "pb_01_table_row3_number2": "7.58", "pb_01_table_row3_number3": "100.0", "pb_01_table_row3_number4": "0.0", "pb_04_table_row1_number1": "8.0", "pb_04_table_row1_number2": "13.0", "pb_04_table_row1_number3": "16.0", "pb_04_table_row2_number1": "2.0", "pb_04_table_row2_number2": "0.0", "pb_04_table_row2_number3": "120.0", "pb_04_table_row3_number1": "10.0", "pb_04