y has its dedicated CSR committee. But CSR committee is not acceptable here.", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "The Company has a robust and comprehensive anti-corruption and anti-bribery policy in place to ensure ethical\\nbusiness practices and maintain the highest standards of integrity across all its operations.\\nhttps://glandpharma.com/images/Anti_Bribery_Policy.pdf", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "The Company, as an Equal Opportunity Employer, is firmly committed to a policy of equal employment opportunity extending to all applicants and employees. It strictly prohibits any form of discrimination on any basis including race, color, creed, sex (including gender harassment and harassment based on pregnancy, childbirth, or related medical condition), religion, marital status, age, national origin or ancestry,\\ndifferently abled, medical condition, sexual orientation, veteran status, or any other category protected by applicable laws, subject to law of land. The Company is committed to provide equal employment opportunities at every stage in the whole gamut of employment or employee lifecycle.", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "The Company places utmost importance on the safety and well-being of its employees and acknowledges\\nthe significance of identifying work-related hazards. To achieve this objective, the Company has implemented\\na robust occupational health and safety management system in alignment with the ISO 45001 standard. This\\ncomprehensive system empowers the Company to proactively manage occupational health and safety risks,\\nensuring a safe and secure working environment for all its employees\\n\\nThe Company has taken proactive measures to ensure workplace safety by implementing a Hazard Identification\\nand Risk Assessment (HIRA) procedure, detailed in SOP GSE024. Through this systematic approach, the Company can effectively identify potential hazards and thoroughly assess the risks associated with them. By conducting these risk assessments, the Company not only enhances workplace safety but also empowers employees to take necessary precautions and implement preventive measures.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "Company does not have other than permanent employees or workers", "pb_23_textarea": "Company does not have other than permanent employees or workers", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "Converted to Gj/crore rupee of turnover", "pb_29_textarea": "Converted to Kl/crore rupee of turnover", "pb_30_textarea": "Converted to Mt/crore rupee of turnover", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "Data was not maintained for 2023.", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "The Company’s commitment to cyber security and data privacy is evident through its well-defined policy accessible\\non the intranet. This framework helps the Company to adhere to best practices, ensuring data protection and fortifying\\nthe Company’s defences against cyber threats.", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_10_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "0.0", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "2", "pb_02_option_number2": "0", "pb_03_option_number1": "11.12", "pb_03_option_number2": "0.0", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "", "pb_05_option_checkbo