well informed about the policy and adherence to the same. External Stakeholders are informed about the applicability and compliance of policy at the time of business association/engagement.", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "Yes. The Policy has been published in the intranet.", "pb_16_textarea": "No Unions existing", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes. Occupational Health and Safety Management System exists.\\nOccupational Health and Safety protection is a integral component of the business. The Company’s goal is to treat\\nthe environment gently and use the natural resources sparingly without hampering the employees occupational\\nHealth and Safety by\\na) Establishing incident free work environment;\\nb) Minimising wastage to prevent natural resources;\\nc) Encouraging innovation for prevention of pollution, injury and ill health;\\nd) Complying with all applicable legal, statutory & regulatory and other required related to Environmental\\nOccupational Health and Safety;\\ne) Ensuring proper disposal of waste/ pollutant/ to minimise impact on environment and risk to employees;\\nf) Continually improving the environmental Occupational Health and Safety performance.\\n\\nFailure Modes and Effects Analysis (FMEA) model\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "false", "pb_29_textarea": "false", "pb_30_textarea": "No such requirements from Govt. bodies.\\n", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "https://www.craftsmanautomation.com/investors/", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "ESG/Sustainability function part of other board committee", "pb_10_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_13_percentage_