169	188	\N	Healthcare	{"pb_01": "information_available", "pb_02": "information_available", "pb_03": "information_available", "pb_04": "information_available", "pb_05": "information_available", "pb_06": "Information Available", "pb_07": "Information available", "pb_08": "information_available", "pb_09": "Information available", "pb_10": "information_available", "pb_11": "information_available", "pb_12": "No clear information", "pb_13": "No information", "pb_14": "information_available", "pb_15": "information_available", "pb_16": "information_available", "pb_17": "information_available", "pb_18": "information_available", "pb_19": "information_available", "pb_20": "information_available", "pb_21": "information_available", "pb_22": "information_available", "pb_23": "information_available", "pb_24": "information_available", "pb_25": "information_available", "pb_26": "information_available", "pb_27": "information_available", "pb_28": "information_available", "pb_29": "information_available", "pb_30": "information_available", "pb_31": "No information", "pb_32": "information_available", "pb_33": "No clear information", "pb_34": "information_available", "pb_35": "information_available", "pb_01_textarea": "", "pb_02_textarea": "", "pb_03_textarea": "", "pb_04_textarea": "", "pb_05_textarea": "https://investor.thyrocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-Whistleblower-Policy_Thyrocare.pdf", "pb_06_textarea": "https://investor.thyrocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Code-of-conduct.pdf", "pb_07_textarea": "https://investor.thyrocare.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Code-of-conduct.pdf", "pb_08_textarea": "The Board of Directors has authorised Mr. Rahul Guha, Managing Director and CEO to take decision on sustainability related issues, in consultation with Senior Managerial Personnel of the Company.", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "Yes, the Company has an Equal Employment Opportunity Policy.\\nThe said policy is available on the intranet of the Company i.e. Drawinbox, HRMS portal of the Company.", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Occupational Health and Safety management the system has been implemented by the Company. Following are some key practices that have been carried out: Monthly inspection of labs of the Company has been conducted.All the labs are under the FireAMC (Annual Maintenance Contract) Maintenance which includes maintenance and servicing of fire equipment on the premises Mock drill trainings are conducted every six months. Safety induction training is given to the new joiners. Personal Protection Equipment kits are provided to the employees deployed at labs, members of maintenance team and also for the ground staff. Daily inspection round in labs is carried out by the Housekeeping Incharge, Canteen Incharge and also by Maintenance team. Segregation of bio-medical waste is ensured as per the regulatory norms prescribed. FirstAid boxes are available at suitable places which is regularly monitored and refilled. Regular Health and Wellness Camps are undertaken for employees. Monthly Safety training is given to the employees on the various safety topics such as chemical handling, manual handling of Materials & equipments, electrical safety, first aid measures & Cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR).\\n\\nWe have developed a Safety Manual that outlines the procedures for identifying and evaluating Safety, Health, and Environment (SH&E) risks, as well as measures to mitigate these risks to acceptable levels. This is achieved by enhancing existing controls or implementing additional controls for all activities within the organization's premises. The manual also clearly defines the roles and responsibilities of all personnel. Additionally, quarterly inspections are conducted across all laboratories to identify potential risks or hazards.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "The policy is available to on the intranet of the Company ie Drawinbox, HRMS portal of the Company.", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "No dedicated board committee, but MD/CEO/CFO/COO or any other executive with multiple responsibilities is also responsible for sustainability issues", "pb_10_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "No it doesn’t", "pb_35_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "", "pb_02_option_number2": "", "pb_03_option_number1": "22.23", "pb_03_option_number2": "0.0", "pb_28_option_checkbox": "", "pb_29_option_checkbox": "", "pb_30_option_checkbox": "", "pb_31_option_checkbox": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox1": "Employees", "pb_05_option_checkbox2": "Workers", "pb_05_option_checkbox3": "", "pb_05_option_checkbox4": "Value chain partners", "pb_05_option_checkbox5": "Customers", "pb_13_option_checkbox2": "", "pb_24_option1_checkbox": "", "pb_06_option1_checkbox1": "Code of conduct for Board of Directors/KMPs", "pb_06_option2_checkbox2": "Code of conduct for employees", "pb_14_option1_checkbox1": "", "pb_20_option1_checkbox1": "Lost Time Injury Frequency Rate", "pb_20_option1_checkbox2": "Fatalities", "pb_01_table_row1_number1": "77.44", "pb_01_table_row1_number2": "22.57", "pb_01_table_row1_number3": "", "pb