it comes to resource allocation.\\n\\nThe committee reviews compliance with regulatory standards and is responsible for approving public disclosures on ESG.", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "Yes, AIA is an equal opportunity employer and has an Equal Opportunity Policy as per the Rights of Persons with Disabilities Act, 2016, which is covered under its HR Manual. This HR Manual is an internal document and is communicated to new hires and relevant parties during the induction and orientation programme.", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes, the organisation is certified under ISO 45001:2018 for Occupational Health & Safety Management System. This certification covers two major plants for grinding media manufacturing located at Moraiya Village and the Kerala GIDC unit at Bavla District, Ahmedabad. The other unit, while not ISO 45001:2018 certified, also adheres to OHS protocols.\\n\\nThe Company uses the HIRA process, i.e., Hazard Identification and Risk Assessment, to identify work-related hazards and assess risks on a routine and non-routine basis, as per ISO 45001:2018.", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "As there are very few female workers, % of their wages is not comparable with Gross wages.", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "", "pb_07_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "Dedicated Board ESG/Sustainability committee", "pb_10_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS man