                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               iv. Employees and workers - https://images.vijayadiagnostic.com/investor/corporategovernance/WHISTLE-BLOWER-POLICY.pdf                                                                                                 v. Customers - The company has a dedicated helpline number (040-21000000/040-6910 0100) and email id info@vijayadiagnostic.com which address and resolves all customer Grievances. In addition, the Company responds to customer concerns that it receives through its official social media handles.                                                                                                                                                  vi. Value Chain Partners - https://images.vijayadiagnostic.com/investor/corporategovernance/WHISTLE-BLOWER-POLICY.pdf", "pb_06_textarea": "Link to the policy - https://images.vijayadiagnostic.com/investor/corporategovernance/CODE-OF-CONDUCT-BOD.pdf", "pb_07_textarea": "Internal policy as they have training and awareness sessions on the same too. ", "pb_08_textarea": "Board of Directors - The CSR Committee of the Board is responsible for taking decisions on sustainability related issues.", "pb_09_textarea": "", "pb_10_textarea": "The Company places a strong emphasis on conducting business in a transparent and ethical manner. To ensure compliance with ethical standards, the Company strictly follows all relevant laws, treaties, and regulations that prohibit bribery and other corrupt activities. The Whistle blower and Code of Conduct Policies, which address ethics, bribery, and fraud/corruption, apply to all Vijaya Group, subsidiaries, and entities. The link to the policy - https://images.vijayadiagnostic.com/investor/corporategovernance/CODE-OF-CONDUCT-BOD.pdf and https://images.vijayadiagnostic.com/investor/corporategovernance/WHISTLE-BLOWER-POLICY.pdf", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "The company is committed to maintaining a policy of non-discrimination and enforcing a strong stance against any behaviours that contravene its ethics and Code of Conduct. These standards are clearly outlined in the Business Responsibility Policy, demonstrating the Company’s dedication to promoting a culture of fairness, respect and accountability. The link to the policy is - https://images.vijayadiagnostic.com/investor/corporategovernance/Business-Responsibility-Policy.pdf", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "Link to the policy - https://www.vijayadiagnostic.com/privacy-policy", "pb_07_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "No board level committee, but CSO or dedicated executive director for sustainability issues", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_19_option_radio": "Company has OHS management system, process to identify & process to report risks", "pb_26_option_radio": "Yes, it does", "pb_35_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option1_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_06_option2_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_12_option_number": "", "pb_33_option_number": "", "pb_02_option_number1": "1", "pb_02_option_number2": "", "pb_03_op