pb_10_textarea": "https://hindware.com/who-we-are/images/Hindware%20Limited_Vigil%20-Whistle-Blower-Policy-Version-II.pdf", "pb_11_textarea": "", "pb_12_textarea": "", "pb_13_textarea": "", "pb_14_textarea": "", "pb_15_textarea": "https://www.hindwarehomes.com/pdf/Business%20Responsibility%20Policies.pdf", "pb_16_textarea": "", "pb_17_textarea": "", "pb_18_textarea": "", "pb_19_textarea": "Yes, HHIL is committed to achieving the highest standards of Health & Safety across the value chain. For our\\noffices across the country, we have already implemented a robust health & safety system. All office buildings\\nare designed to ensure safety and are equipped with safety systems such as fire detection, firefighting system,\\nsafe means of escape, assembly points emergency evacuation plans, etc. We regularly impart safety training\\nto our workforce to build a culture of safety in the organisation.\\n\\nWe have conducted a comprehensive Hazard Identification and Risk Assessment (HIRA) study to identify and\\nassess risks associated with work-related hazards. HIRA process is followed to identify work-related hazards\\nfor all routine & non-routine activities. Based on the severity of risks, we take mitigation measures as per the\\nhierarchy of risk controls such as engineering, administrative, and PPE controls, etc.\\n\\nYes\\n\\nYes", "pb_20_textarea": "", "pb_21_textarea": "", "pb_22_textarea": "", "pb_23_textarea": "", "pb_24_textarea": "", "pb_25_textarea": "", "pb_26_textarea": "Yes", "pb_27_textarea": "", "pb_28_textarea": "", "pb_29_textarea": "", "pb_30_textarea": "", "pb_31_textarea": "", "pb_32_textarea": "", "pb_33_textarea": "", "pb_34_textarea": "", "pb_35_textarea": "https://www.hindwarehomes.com/privacy-policy.php", "pb_07_option_radio": "Publicly available Policy", "pb_08_option_radio": "ESG/Sustainability function part of other board committee", "pb_10_option_radio": "Internal Policy", "pb_13_percentage_1": "", "pb_13_percentage_2": "", "pb_15_option_radio